lead_paragraph: AC Milan lifted the Italian Super Cup after 17-year-old goalkeeper Gianluigi Donnarumma's save from Paulo Dybala secured a 4-3 penalty shootout win over Juventus on Friday.

headline.print_headline: Donnarumma Save Wins Super Cup for Milan
